"The user browses View 1 at the Overview level and learns about the overall sales distribution across daily, weekly, and monthly time granularities. Next, the user brushes a specific time range in View 1, and observes that Views 2, 4, and 6 are updated accordingly. In View 2, the user explores daily and cumulative sales trends using the area chart. Then, the user drills down into holiday effects in View 3 and category-level sales contributions in View 4. Additionally, marketing influence on selected periods is analyzed in depth in View 6 through a scatter plot."